msgstr "规范 API 名称：`ptool.s3.Connection:list`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/s3.md:157
msgid "`conn:list([prefix])` lists entries under a prefix and returns a dense Lua array table."
msgstr "`conn:list([prefix])` 列出某个前缀下的条目，并返回致密 Lua 数组表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/s3.md:160
msgid "`prefix` (string, optional): The prefix to list. Defaults to the connection root."
msgstr "`prefix`（string，选填）：要列出的前缀。默认为连接根路径。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/s3.md:162
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/s3.md:162"
